pullRequest.title: Misc fixes for cosmos public surface APIs
pullRequest.bodyText:
Rename CosmosResponseDiagnostics -> CosmosDiagnostics : #11261
Fixed Stored Proc execute() API: #11260
Rename API - connectionSharingAcrossClientsEnabled
Added @warning annotation to *BridgeInternal classes
Rename getRequestLatency() -> getDuration()
Hide sessionCapturingOverrideEnabled API CosmosClientBuilder
Hide setConsistencyLevel / getConsistencyLevel from public surface *RequestOptions
Removed jackson dependency from pom.xml - taking from azure-core now.

commit.message: Misc fixes for cosmos public surface APIs

nodes.bodyText: maybe we should mention that these may change in future.
